{"title":"Silca Launches Grinta Fastpacking Handlebar and Seat Bags","link":"https://theradavist.com/silca-grinta-fastpacking-bags/","date":1710432001000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03415-medium.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03415-medium.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03415-medium.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03415-medium.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03415-medium.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Today our friends at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9c3967ea-9801-442a-9d09-419007ae71c3&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsilca.cc%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Silca</a> launch their first collection of fastpacking adventure bags, the Grinta bags. This thoughtfully designed set, comprised of a handlebar bag and a roll top seat pack, embodies Silca’s commitment to performance, functionality, and rider experience, catering to both competition and casual exploration.<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"1080\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/grintaunpack.gif?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Drawing inspiration from the success of the Mattone Seat Packs, the Grinta Bags incorporate the proven BOA closure system for a secure and adjustable fit. This attention to detail ensures the bags stay put, even on the most demanding rides.</p>\n<p>Whether you are an ultra-endurance rider or simply seeking a versatile solution for extended days on the road, The Grinta Bags have you covered. The easily accessible handlebar bag keeps essentials readily available, while the roll-top expandable seat pack can handle fast day packing, up to overnight adventure rides, as well as ultra distance gravel events. The seat pack shields gear from the elements and wind, while its seam-welded weatherproof construction guarantees worry-free rides.</p>\n<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03352-medium.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03352-medium.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03352-medium.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03352-medium.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC03352-medium.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/barbagwide-medium.jpg?fit=1200,1067&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/barbagwide-medium.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/barbagwide-medium.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/barbagwide-medium.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/barbagwide-medium.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9c3967ea-9801-442a-9d09-419007ae71c3&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsilca.cc%2Fproducts%2Fgrinta-handlebar-bag\" target=\"_blank\">Grinta Handlebar Bag</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>2-liter capacity</li>\n<li>Features secure, one-handed operation with the Magic Slide no-slip strap and buckle system.</li>\n<li>Constructed from durable CYCLEPET fabric</li>\n<li>YKK AquaGuard zipper for water resistance</li>\n<li>$95 USD / €115</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/DSC0